e APM cluster sample.\nThe observed variation of correlation length with richness agrees well with the\nmodels, particularly for $\\Lambda$CDM. The observed power spectrum (for a\ncluster sample of mean separation $d_{\\rm c}=31h^{-1}$Mpc) lies significantly\nabove the predictions of both models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 May 2000 23:03:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Jul 2000 08:55:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-25"}
