ive is that HIPASS J1712-64\nwas ejected from the interacting Magellanic Cloud/Galaxy system at\nperigalacticon ~ 2 x 10^8 yr ago.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 May 2000 06:12:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
