ffects and, even then, not all name confusion would be\nsettled. A ``modest proposal'' is made that our professional field (and others)\ngo to a system of uniquely associating an identification number to each author\non each paper to solve the name confusion problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 May 2000 14:40:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Jun 2000 08:29:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
